Detailed Description

Stores gaunt coefficients and offsite overlap integral factors. Access as l1, l2, (L-|l1-l2|)/2, l1+m1, m2. Constrained by l1 >= l2, m2 >= 0, L >= |l1-l2|, L <= l1+l2
